 Do’s                                        

• Think before you post                                         
•  Curate a positive, useful feed                   
•  Protect your privacy and accounts                          
•  Set clear time limits for scrolling          
•  Use social media to build real connections 

-------------------------------------------------------------
Don’ts

•  Don’t overshare personal info 
•  Don’t compare your life to others’ posts  
•  Don’t join or fuel online drama 
•  Don’t post while very emotional or intoxicated
•  Don’t ignore how social media affects your mood 
